24:27.299 --> 24:31.137
(eerie chanting)

24:32.839 --> 24:34.874
(high-pitched screaming)

24:34.907 --> 24:37.544
(chanting continues)

24:39.211 --> 24:43.282
(singing in foreign language)

24:43.315 --> 24:46.385
(woman warbling)

24:46.418 --> 24:48.387
(hissing)

24:48.420 --> 24:49.355
(flames roaring)

24:49.388 --> 24:50.857
-Oh!
-Aaah!

24:50.890 --> 24:53.626
ANNOUNCER:
What We Do in the Shadows.

24:53.660 --> 24:56.495
All new
Wednesdays at 10:00 on FX.

24:58.330 --> 25:00.232
MAN: Five, six, seven, eight.

25:00.266 --> 25:02.969
-He's a wonderful teacher.
-Boom-chicka-boom.

25:03.002 --> 25:04.571
Well, you have
taught him plenty.

25:04.604 --> 25:06.739
When do I find out
if I got the part or not?

25:06.773 --> 25:08.708
You got the part
when you walked in the door.

25:08.741 --> 25:10.209
ANNOUNCER: Fosse/Verdon.

25:10.242 --> 25:13.045
All new, Tuesday at 10:00,
only on FX.

25:15.447 --> 25:16.716
(grunts)

25:18.117 --> 25:19.852
This is just-- This is--

25:19.886 --> 25:22.555
(grunts) Seriously?

25:22.589 --> 25:23.455
Whoo.

25:26.959 --> 25:28.527
Who's the lucky guy?

25:29.562 --> 25:31.163
ANNOUNCER: Better Things.

25:31.197 --> 25:33.032
All new
Thursdays at 10:00 on FX.

25:36.368 --> 25:39.171
(shrieks)
Rocket pack!

25:39.205 --> 25:41.540
You know how much fuel
you just wasted?

25:41.574 --> 25:45.444
Oh, no. How much paint
did Michelangelo waste
on the Sistine Chapel?

25:45.477 --> 25:47.446
ANNOUNCER: Archer 1999.

25:47.479 --> 25:50.316
